room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Mountain Room Escapes in Big Bear City
room_address: 40729 Village Dr, Suite 6, Big Bear Lake, CA 92315
room_description: You and your friends are hiking in the woods when you come across an abandoned cabin. The front door is open, so you decide to explore. As soon as you step in the door, it slams behind you. Something truly terrifying is waiting inside. Can you escape before it is too late?
